\State Update the combination weights: $(w_m^k)_{i+1} = (w_m^k)_{i}\sum_{y_{ij} \in D_{val}^{k*}}\frac{\hat{f}_m(y_{i,j})}{\sum_{l=1}^{M}\hat{f}_l(y_{i,j})(w_l^k)_{i}}$
